Would've probably been six at Chinnaswamy but the boundaries at Barabati slightly bigger. Also, Jadeja slowed it down nicely, hit a good length to ensure Lewis didn't get underneath the delivery. The bat face turned in his hand as he swung through, so didn't get the power he would've liked. Good catch under pressure.

commentary: Paul to Kohli, OUT plays it on! Keemo Paul injecting life into this contest every time he comes on! It is an innocuous delivery though, not unlike the one that got Pant. Kohli falls short of the finish line
